        <num>CC 623</num>
        <heading>623.  Abuse of the enjoyment; consequences</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 623.  Abuse of the enjoyment; consequences
The usufruct may be terminated by the naked owner if the usufructuary commits waste, alienates things without authority, neglects to make ordinary repairs, or abuses his enjoyment in any other manner.</p>
        </content>
